    "body" : "<p>There are workarounds but no clean/short/sweet way to do it with streams and to be honest, you would probably be better off with:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int idx = 0;\nfor (Param p : params) query.bind(idx++, p);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Or the older style:</p>\n\n<pre><code>for (int idx = 0; idx &lt; params.size(); idx++) query.bind(idx, params.get(idx));\n</code></pre>\n"
